    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Reduced Cost: 3 Sage Chakra</p><p>You use Sage Chakra to create bombs of oscillating energy of your description and personal design. Select a target within range. Make a ranged Senjutsu attack.</p><p>On a hit, you deal 10d12 Force damage and target creature must succeed a Wisdom Saving throw being blinded and deafened until the end of their next turn on a failed save.</p><p>Creatures who are targeted by this Art are left with an imprint of your chakra. The next attack made targeting a creature targeted by this Art is made at advantage, afterwards, the imprint vanishes.</p><p>Sage Affinity Synergy: If you have the Reptilian Senjutsu class mod feature, when you cast this Senjutsu, you may utilize the techniques that your tribe has entrusted you with. If you do, you can create up to two additional constructs targeting either the same or additional creatures. For each additional construct targeting one creature, you instead increase the damage dealt by +4 and reduce the targets saving throw by -1.</p>",
